listing.name: Luxury Houseboat, Beautiful Setting
listing.access: Guests have access to the entire boat and terrace.
listing.description:
Beautiful 2 bedroom on the river Amstel with secure entrance. A large open plan living space. If you want a place to relax after a long day or week you will find it here with easy links into central Amsterdam.

Situated in the heart of Amsterdam near historic sites and pubs. Extraordinary views. Beautifully finished interior. Large kitchen fully equipped, large bathroom for showering and fully functioning marine loo. Great beds for sweet dreams!

Spectacular views, historical sites, friendly locals, beautiful swans, and chatty geese and ducks! Right across the famous Amstel Hotel.

Guests have access to the entire boat and terrace.

There will be a personal host waiting for you upon arrival. They will stand ready to answer any questions you may have.

From Schiphol, take the train to Amsterdam Centraal. From there take tram 51, 53, or 54 and get off at Weesperplein. It is a 3 minute stroll to the boat from there.
listing.house_rules:
-no smoking or drugs allowed
-no pets allowed
-no party’s
-please respect the neighbours and the neighbourhood
-please lock the doors when you leave

review.comments: This was an excellent houseboat for a short stay. On our deck we had a duck sitting on 2 eggs 24/7 - it was very entertaining watching it! This is a real home, equipped with everything! There was a lot of space, 2 bedrooms, large bathroom, big living room and kitchen. Thank you Timon! Communication was smooth and everything went great! Will book it again next time we come to Amsterdam. (note: not super centralized, but there's a tram station right on the corner or uber always available)
